## Sample Call Graph

```mermaid
graph LR
{%- set seen = [] %}
{%- for rel in relations[:50] %}
{%- if rel.type.value == "calls" %}
{%- set src = rel.source_id.split("/")[-1].split(":")[-1] %}
{%- set tgt = rel.target_id.split(":")[-1] %}
{%- set edge = src + "-->" + tgt %}
{%- if edge not in seen and src and tgt and src != tgt %}
{%- set _ = seen.append(edge) %}
    {{ src }} --> {{ tgt }}
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- endfor %}
```

